title: Steve Wilkos A Stormy Past
description:
A STORMY PAST:
    --------------
    Did she do it? Stormy's foster sister Belinda has accused her of molesting her young daughters. An accusation Stormy says is not only inconceivable, but ruining her life. She's here to clear her name and learn the truth behind Belinda's accusations. Jane, Belinda's mother, also believes Stormy to be guilty, and wants her to stop the act, and face up to what she did. The truth well be revealed, because Steve's had them all take lie detector tests, and there's nowhere left to hide.
